  "texts": [
    "One limitation of this work is that the faithfulness of Chain-of-Thought reasoning has not been extensively studied, and our analysis relies on faithfulness metrics that are still in the early stages of development.",
    "As these metrics evolve, our findings may need to be revisited.",
    "Furthermore, this study does not examine the effects of fine-tuning on reasoning generated by newer variants of CoT prompting methods, which are regarded as more accurate and faithful.",
    "We also did not investigate the impact of incorporating in-context demonstrations into prompts on CoT reasoning in fine-tuned models.",
    "Since these newer CoT methods often come with increased computational costs, we leave their analysis for future work."
  ],
